data.description: Seller will accept or counter offers between $629,000- $659,000. Welcome to your unique ''Consuelo'' designed floor plan. GORGEOUS kitchen featuring waterfall granite island, custom hammered copper sink (matching sink in the private guest casita), Tasteful backsplash w/pot filler over gourmet gas range, SS appliance package, frosted barn door pantry, cozy breakfast nook w/coffee/espresso bar. Open floor plan w/loads of natural light, vaulted ceilings. Inviting courtyard leads to private guest casita, spacious backyard w/extended covered patio, fireplace and grill area, relaxing water feature, mountain views. Energy savings w/solar system. Amazingly remodeled and impeccably maintained. Finished garage w/tons of storage. Great opportunity for an assumable loan at a great rate. WOW!
